</p>

</div>
<div id="fn" class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#GEWN-03-03-02-0368-fn-0001-ptr" id="GEWN-03-03-02-0368-fn-0001">1</a>

   <p>See <a href="default.xqy?keys=GEWN-print-03-03-02-0277" class="document">GW to Schuyler, 27 Feb. 1776</a>.</p>

</div>
<div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#GEWN-03-03-02-0368-fn-0002-ptr" id="GEWN-03-03-02-0368-fn-0002">2</a>

   <p>The <abbr title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ Handwritten copies in one of the bound volumes used by the team of clerks on GW's headquarters staff who worked from 1781-83 under the direction of Lt. Col. Richard Varick to record correspondence, orders, instructions, and related items from GWs Revolutionary War papers ]">Varick transcript</abbr> mistakenly reads on the 15th. For the fortification of Nooks Hill, see <a href="default.xqy?keys=GEWN-print-03-03-02-0363" class="document">GW to Hancock</a> and <a href="default.xqy?keys=GEWN-print-03-03-02-0366" class="document">GW to Joseph Reed, both 19 Mar. 1776</a>.</p>

</div>
<div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#GEWN-03-03-02-0368-fn-0003-ptr" id="GEWN-03-03-02-0368-fn-0003">3</a>

   <p>See <a href="default.xqy?keys=GEWN-print-03-03-02-0390-0002" class="document">Inventory of British Stores Left in Boston, 20 Mar.</a>,<span class="choice deletion" title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover_choice ] header=[]  body=[ Deleted: ' printed below as' &lt;span style='font-size: 90%'&gt;[[2014-12-02]]&lt;/span&gt; ]"><img alt="deletion" src="images/deletion_mark-trans.png" style="border:none;vertical-align: text-bottom; padding-right:2px"/></span> an enclosure to <a href="default.xqy?keys=GEWN-print-03-03-02-0390-0001" class="document">GW to Hancock, 24 Mar. 1776</a>, and <a href="default.xqy?keys=GEWN-print-03-03-02-0409-0002" class="document">Return of British Ordnance Stores Left in Boston, 22 Mar.</a>, printed as an enclosure to <a href="default.xqy?keys=GEWN-print-03-03-02-0409-0001" class="document">GW to Hancock, 27 Mar. 1776</a>.</p>

</div>
<div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#GEWN-03-03-02-0368-fn-0004-ptr" id="GEWN-03-03-02-0368-fn-0004">4</a>

   <p>See <a href="default.xqy?keys=GEWN-print-03-03-02-0222-0001&amp;expandNote=GEWN-03-03-02-0222-0001-fn-0004#GEWN-03-03-02-0222-0001-fn-0004" class="document">GW to Hancock, 14 Feb. 1776, and note 4</a>.</p>

